the tail's stopped moving.

215
00:12:50,368 --> 00:12:52,470
[Rui Prieto] Yeah it's,
it, it's called gliding.

216
00:12:52,506 --> 00:12:55,375
They use the, the, the
momentum that they have

217
00:12:55,407 --> 00:12:57,408
