228
00:13:25,871 --> 00:13:27,238
[Rui Prieto] Yeah.

229
00:13:28,407 --> 00:13:31,409
[James Cameron] Sperm whales
use sound to hunt in the dark.

230
00:13:31,444 --> 00:13:34,947
[clicking]

231
