235
00:13:51,497 --> 00:13:52,264
you notice that?

236
00:13:52,798 --> 00:13:55,100
[Rui Prieto] Yeah. Yeah. The,
the water is becoming clearer.

237
00:13:55,135 --> 00:13:56,868
[James Cameron]
No luck this time,

238
